data.description: Seller financing preferred! This charming 2 bedroom, 1 bath home is updated and ready for it's next owner! This beautiful home has been tastefully renovated including an updated kitchen with shaker cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The bathroom also has modern updates including a new vanity, tile, paint and lighting. The outside of the home was painted in 2021, and has just been freshly painted inside throughout. The HVAC and water heater were installed in 2021 and the roof was installed in 2020. The home has a BONUS space off the kitchen, perfect for a home office, play room, sitting area or dining space. The home boasts a large fully fenced in backyard with covered patio - the perfect spot to entertain friends and family! A single car attached garage provides shelter for your vehicle from the sun or ample room for storage and the long driveway also accommodates additional parking space. Conveniently located close to downtown St. Pete, local dining and shopping! Call today for your private showing!
